              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/775a72af4465a157d3769ee561744b61_5509093168836556539.png",
                "id": "talent62233",
                "key": "风轮两立",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风轮两立"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">夜叉傩面</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/447838f91bec368a2772f63aaa927c4c_5530364999482145061.png",
                "id": "talent44399",
                "key": "靖妖傩舞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "靖妖傩舞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷元素伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_545980287038129725.png",
                "id": "talent15746",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">夜叉傩面</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，且角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色进行下落攻击时：</span>伤害额外+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色为出战角色，我方执行「切换角色」行动时：</span>少花费1个元素骰。（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">下落攻击</span></strong></p><p>角色被切换为「出战角色」后，本回合内的下一个战斗行动若为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「普通攻击」</span>，则被被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「下落攻击」</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1150850679857544908.png",
